---
title: Mexican Chicken Wraps with Potato Wedges and Apple & Beetroot Slaw
description: These Mexican chicken wraps are accompanied by a slaw that's as colourful as it is delicious. Apple, carrot and beetroot combine to make a pretty-in-pink salad that's earthy, sweet and pack's a crunch. Here's a tip for preparing it without looking like Lady Macbeth: before peeling and grating the beetroot, rub some oil over your hands. It will help prevent staining and keep the colour on the plate!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-chicken-wraps-7fa8dd3a.jpg
